# Changelog

## v1.1.0 - Plugin Renamed to AvoMailToForm
- Renamed plugin from **Send It Form** to **AvoMailToForm**
- Updated all references in documentation and settings

## v1.0.0 - Initial Beta Release  
- Added SMTP support for sending emails via Brevo  
- Integrated Google reCAPTCHA v2 & v3 for spam prevention  
- Enabled Akismet spam filtering for added security  
- Implemented AJAX form submission for a smooth user experience  
- Created WordPress admin settings panel for easy configuration  
